    {"type":"arrow","version":1,"versionNonce":1312,"isDeleted":false,"id":"arr-s34","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":950,"y":515,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":20,"height":0,"seed":1312,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":2},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"startBinding":null,"endBinding":null,"lastCommittedPoint":null,"startArrowhead":null,"endArrowhead":"arrow","points":[[0,0],[20,0]]},

    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1400,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-title","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":670,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":900,"height":28,"seed":1400,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":20,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Score breakdown — base 50, capped at 100","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"st","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1500,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-1","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":710,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","width":290,"height":210,"seed":1500,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1501,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-1-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":724,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":258,"height":190,"seed":1501,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Community traction\n\nholdersCount > 100   +15\nholdersCount > 30    +8\nholdersCount > 10    +4\n\nA fresh launch with 100+ holders\nin under 60 seconds means real\norganic interest, not one-wallet\nself-trade.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sc1","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1600,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":350,"y":710,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","width":290,"height":210,"seed":1600,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1601,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-2-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":366,"y":724,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":258,"height":190,"seed":1601,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Low concentration\n\ndevHoldings   < 5%   +10\nsnipersHoldings < 5% +10\ntop10Holdings < 30%  +10\ntop10Holdings < 50%  +5\n\nLow concentration = lower rug\nrisk and more upside room. The\ngate already rejects 15/20/70%,\nthis rewards the truly clean ones.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sc2","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1700,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-3","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":660,"y":710,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","width":290,"height":210,"seed":1700,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1701,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-3-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":676,"y":724,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":258,"height":190,"seed":1701,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Pool growth\n\nliquidityMax / liquidity > 1.5\n  → +5\n\nThe pool was bigger at some point\nthan it is now-or-equal, meaning\nbuy pressure exists. A pool that\nonly shrinks since launch is a\nslow rugpull.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sc3","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":1800,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-4","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":970,"y":710,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#fff9db","width":290,"height":210,"seed":1800,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1801,"isDeleted":false,"id":"score-4-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":986,"y":724,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":258,"height":190,"seed":1801,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Launch maturity\n\nbondingPercentage > 20%   +5\nproTradersCount   > 5     +5\ntrendingScore1min > 0     +5\n\nDoes the launch have momentum?\n  bonding %   = how filled the\n                 curve is\n  proTraders  = wallets Mobula\n                 tags as good\n  trendingScore = Mobula's own\n                 ranking signal","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sc4","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":1900,"isDeleted":false,"id":"section-2","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":960,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":600,"height":32,"seed":1900,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":22,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Pulse Stream V2 — wire format","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sec2","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":2000,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-sub","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":1000,"strokeColor":"#e8590c","backgroundColor":"#ffe8cc","width":420,"height":340,"seed":2000,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":2001,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-sub-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":1012,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":392,"height":320,"seed":2001,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Subscribe (client → server, after open)\n\n{\n  type: 'pulse-v2',\n  authorization: <API_KEY>,\n  payload: {\n    assetMode: true,\n    compressed: false,\n    views: [{\n      name: 'fresh-tokens',\n      chainId: ['solana:solana','evm:8453','evm:1'],\n      poolTypes: ['pumpfun','raydium-v4',\n                  'uniswap-v2','uniswap-v3'],\n      sortBy: 'created_at',\n      sortOrder: 'desc',\n      limit: 50,\n      filters: {\n        liquidity: { gte: 2000 },\n        bonded:    { equals: false }\n      }\n    }]\n  }\n}\n\nNote: chainId / poolTypes go INSIDE the view,\nnot in payload.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sub","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":2100,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-msgs","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":480,"y":1000,"strokeColor":"#c92a2a","backgroundColor":"#ffe3e3","width":420,"height":340,"seed":2100,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":2101,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-msgs-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":496,"y":1012,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":392,"height":320,"seed":2101,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":13,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Server messages (server → client)\n\ninit\n  { type, payload: { 'fresh-tokens':\n                     { data: [row, ...] } } }\n  → seed dedup, do NOT alert\n\nsync (~every 30s)\n  same shape as init\n  → REPLACE state, not merge\n\nnew-token\n  { type, payload:\n     { viewName, token: row } }\n  → dedup, score, alert\n\nupdate-token / remove-token\n  ignored (no first-alert relevance)\n\nrow is FLAT: address, chainId, symbol,\nliquidity, bonded, devHoldings,\nsnipersHoldings, top10Holdings, ...","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"msgs","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":2200,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-quirks","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":920,"y":1000,"strokeColor":"#5f3dc4","backgroundColor":"#e5dbff","width":340,"height":340,"seed":2200,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":2201,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-quirks-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":936,"y":1012,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":312,"height":320,"seed":2201,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":14,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Things that bit us\n\n1. chainId / poolTypes must sit\n   INSIDE the view object,\n   not in payload.\n\n2. Top-level field is `payload`,\n   not `data`.\n\n3. Init/sync data lives at\n   payload['fresh-tokens'].data\n\n4. Token row is flat:\n   devHoldings (NOT\n   devHoldingsPercentage)\n   top10Holdings, snipersHoldings.\n\n5. Init = current view state,\n   not new launches.\n   Use it to seed dedup, never\n   to alert.\n\n6. Subscriptions don't persist\n   on reconnect — re-subscribe.","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"quirks","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":2300,"isDeleted":false,"id":"section-3","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":1380,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":600,"height":32,"seed":2300,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":22,"fontFamily":3,"text":"Video script — 7 beats","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"sec3","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25},

    {"type":"rectangle","version":1,"versionNonce":2400,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-script","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":2,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":40,"y":1420,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"#f8f9fa","width":1220,"height":380,"seed":2400,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":{"type":3},"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false},
    {"type":"text","version":1,"versionNonce":2401,"isDeleted":false,"id":"box-script-text","fillStyle":"solid","strokeWidth":1,"strokeStyle":"solid","roughness":0,"opacity":100,"angle":0,"x":56,"y":1436,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","backgroundColor":"transparent","width":1192,"height":360,"seed":2401,"groupIds":[],"frameId":null,"roundness":null,"boundElements":[],"updated":1,"link":null,"locked":false,"fontSize":15,"fontFamily":3,"text":"1. The problem\n   Sniping fresh tokens is a race. By the time DexScreener lists a token, the move is already over.\n   You need the data BEFORE the public indexers do.\n\n2. Why Pulse Stream V2\n   One WebSocket. Every chain Mobula supports. Every DEX (pump.fun, Moonshot, Raydium, Uniswap).\n   Server-side filters: liquidity, bonded, holdings concentration, sort, limit. The wire is already clean.\n\n3. Architecture\n   Show the four boxes: PulseClient · SeenStore · QualityGate · Formatter+Bot. ~600 lines, no infra.\n\n4. The decision pipeline (key beat)\n   Walk through the 4 stages: server filter → dedup → reject gates → score & send.\n   First failure exits silently. Only stage 4 produces a message.\n\n5. Live demo\n   npm run dev. Logs: connecting → connected → subscribed. Wait for first new-token line.\n   Switch to Telegram, alert appears. Click Chart → DexScreener. Click Trade on pump.fun → token page.\n\n6. Resilience\n   Auto-reconnect with exponential backoff. Re-subscribe on every reconnect.\n   SQLite dedup so the periodic sync replay never double-alerts.\n   Init snapshot is silent — only live new-token events become Telegram messages.\n\n7. Closing\n   Built on Mobula Pulse — the same stream used by exchanges and trading desks.\n   Code is open-source under MIT. Repo: github.com/Flotapponnier/pulse-sniper","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","containerId":null,"originalText":"script","autoResize":true,"lineHeight":1.25}
  ],
  "appState": {
    "gridSize": null,
    "viewBackgroundColor": "#ffffff"
  },
